  "body": "<div id=\"post-view221240815866\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea221240815866\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">안녕하세요~&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">저번주 토요일에 받은&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">엄청 맛있는 떡과 에그타르트에요</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">환자분께서 우리 이수한의원 식구들을 위해 맛있는걸 사다주셨어요</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">쇠머리떡, 모듬배기찰떡과 에그타르트죠~</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f80f91b89107fe91.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 550px;\" id=\"MjAxODAzMzBfMTEw/MDAxNTIyMzcyMTk1MTU0.r6M_S6Sa9tAICiqeeWe2b_xWi-q6zhTcNKOgSoTJ3kwg.CHUjwFbyGds6hASWJyA2f3RtremZ0_h7CgZLbJArtdQg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20180330_093132709.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003382FAF0FA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" 