Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">쫄깃쫄깃하고</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">적당히 달달하고</span></p><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">콩 호박 밤 등 때문에 몸에 좋은 건강한 맛이었어요</span></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/67d59151baeb65c8.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth: 550px; rheight: 550px;\" id=\"MjAxODAzMzBfMjE1/MDAxNTIyMzcyMTk1NDUz.0jg1DCrsrkQq5AwyKv3Meref9azuX3FS54eDPWeAaNIg.BGSclmSNh0v0gWXpMjriht94YtDbfDAZFsKl_g2Eekcg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20180330_093133096.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003382FAF0FA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/67d59151baeb65c8.jpg\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">﻿</span></div><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim;\"><br /></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">에그타르트는 항상 맛있구요!ㅎㅎ</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim;\"><br /></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim;\"><br /></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim;\"><br /></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">환자분 덕분에 너무 맛있게 잘먹었습니다 ^^ 감사합니다&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim;\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/line_choco\" target=\"_b